 of mana for my lvl... (i can cast a lot before needing to med, and thats NOT including the 'dark pact, vamperic embrace, life spike) combo<br><br>ANY ADVICE for a lvl 9 necro, please post or mail me, under my profile. Subject NECRO<br><br>Pentaganomicon on Terris-thule<br>Valdon - lvl 25 cleric Terris-thule</p>&nbsp;<br> 'Valdon Gravedancer' Terris-Thule. Dwarven Cleric 32nd season.<br> 'Junglebug Sugarpants' Terris-Thule. Halfling Druid. 39th season.<br> 'Shinook Eldergod' Terris-Thule. Troll Shaman of 32nd season</td></td></tr>
