	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=103668><span id=Sage>Ishtarra</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>25 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.50]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Let's see if I can cover most popular Necro questions.<br><br>Charisma has a minor affect on charm but no affect on fear spells.&nbsp;&nbsp;The higher the cha, the better you are at charming.  Your level matters more on charm than your cha, though.<br><br>Mana regen thru the med skill caps at 15 points/tick at level 50 at max med skill and then scales one point each level to 25 points/tick at level 60.  This is the same for all casters except Bards.<br><br>Research spell components drop off mobs of similar level.  So, if you need level 49 research spell components, they drop off mobs level 46+.  Goto to zones with those mobs in them and you can get your words.  You can also check vendors and buy the words people sold to them.<br><br>What race necro is the best?  It depends.  Play the race you think fits you best.  If you are a power gamer, most choose Iksar due to their inate regeneration.  In the end game, this is vey nice to have.  But, the person playing the necro is more important than the race of the necro.  <br><br>HP are nice for Necros.  In the end game, you will accumulate plus HP items.  There are uber necros with over 2500 unbuffed HP...but those are rare.  Much more common are 2000 plus unbuffed HP.<br><br>Necros are great in groups.  People who tell you otherwise are ignorant of what a necro can do.  In the end game, necros do more than pump manna.  We do lots of damage, especially in long fights.<br><br>And to the dork Ranger who shot arrows at the Warlock(see his post below)...ROFLMAO...that was Lifeburn baby!!  You should choose fights you can win.  Also, spell criticals can do up to double damage...so unless a necro uses an EE for a tap, their max crit with lifetap is 1440.  With an EE, they can get 2200.<br><br>And finally, there are peeps who would argue with any or all of my points.  If you like playing a necro...it really does not matter what random_dumbass_00 thinks, play your class well and people will respect and fear you.<br><br>Ishtarra Gemeinseele<br>Warlock of the Dirty Soul<br>Uber N00b Extraordinaire<br>Tunare Server</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
